Willow Lakes RV & Golf Resort is a gated, 55+ community for active adults.
Willow Lakes RV & Golf Resort (“Willow Lakes”) is a gated RV resort with a beautifully maintained executive golf course.  Willow Lakes  is conveniently located in the city of Titusville on the east coast of central Florida. This region is referred to as the Space Coast. Willow Lakes is minutes from world famous Cape Canaveral (Port Canaveral), Cocoa Beach, Daytona Beach and Disney World!
Willow Lakes residents can watch and feel rocket launches within 5 miles of Cape Canaveral.  RV enthusiasts enjoy an active, adult lifestyle at Willow Lakes.  You can rent or own an RV Port Home, RV Cottage Home, RV Executive Suite, RV Lot or you may decide to CUSTOM BUILD your seasonal getaway!
At Willow Lakes RV & Golf Resort, the dreaded life of shoveling snow, congested city life, and traffic jams become a by-gone memory.  Live 15 minutes from pristine sand beaches, nature preserves, spacious rivers, walking trails, and leave that hectic stress-filled life behind.
Less than one hour ride to Orlando, Florida.  Orlando is a world-class destination for shoppers, golfers, hospitality conventions, theme parks, and and two international airports.
At Willow Lakes, enjoy easy living with one small maintenance fee of $215.00 per month.  This $215.00 fee pays for WI-FI internet access, water, sewer, trash removal, year-round lawn mowing/edging, over 100 channels of HDTV cable and all on-site amenities.
